methods: abstract Set<String> getCriticalExtensionOIDs() Returns the set of OIDs of the extension(s) marked as CRITICAL, that this implementation manages.
abstract byte[] getExtensionValue(String oid) Returns the extension value as DER-encoded OCTET string for the specified OID.
abstract Set<String> getNonCriticalExtensionOIDs() Returns the set of OIDs of the extension(s) marked as NON-CRITICAL, that this implementation manages.
abstract boolean hasUnsupportedCriticalExtension() Returns whether this instance has an extension marked as CRITICAL that it cannot support.
